{
  "stem": "4276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the mother was right away, the girl-- this daughter of hers, got to Plaszow and to take place of her mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they allowed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And these two girls were hanged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I couldn't go back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was when the ghetto was-- it was in '43, has to be in-- had to be in '43, something like beginning of '43.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so this woman that was taking care of us for two, two nights, she said she cannot keep us any longer because her, her husband's brother was crazy.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he might walk around and spill that we are there, spill the news.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we went to the place where we stayed for big money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when the money was gone and that when they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] found the jewelry and everything, then they told my aunt, you'd better get out with both of them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we don't want to have you here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- we will call the Gestapo to come for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had-- again, we stayed on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from one to the other, somehow, she found everybody, you know, [LAUGHS] but only for one night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I told her, you know what, how about if we go on Gentile papers?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she found a place where she could get for us papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I, I just don't know where I putted them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if you need the papers, I will look and send it to you, OK?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
